{"tid":486720,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恆生指數呢個發明真係好撚on9","createTime":"2017-12-02T06:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T05:25:18.000Z","uid":84159,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4cca532b3d24635e937e8aee39f9772af2b46207","tid":486720,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"老實講句 某隻恆生指數股大升/大跌 關其他唔同行業既股乜事先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解依加你幾十隻大股圍威喂 夾條指數出黎 就算其他股同隻大股原全冇關係 你升你跌 都影響埋人地個升跌先 公平咩? <br />\n<br />\n呢個指數根本冇參考價值(包含個幾十隻另計) 都唔知點解個個都睇住佢做買賣 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：恆指大跌個時一定驚撚到仆街人踩人式走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e57b4bb10b3d7fb3c7e43957180407b8f733e6c","tid":486720,"uid":82587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"dji得30 隻股,係咪更圍威喂"},{"pid":"0fe650e9ca3e2cd410f94ddb2de819da16442f9c","tid":486720,"uid":131298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:12:42.000Z","msg":"係，宜家好多股都跟跌唔跟升，勁on9"},{"pid":"a03e8b9eb77704eb23dc2621e043c83d5f8893fc","tid":486720,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"仲要國企都撈一大堆。完全同香港無咩關係sosad。香港公司又有堆係外國公司。總之就係亂。無得預方向。"},{"pid":"52498ce088de1c35dc6625209b33388ee2203777","tid":486720,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:15:21.000Z","msg":"股票依個發仲ON9 間公司生意好唔好同股值有咩關係先"},{"pid":"08a9d787da144c64247f4d2292ea8d16ed3770c0","tid":486720,"uid":131298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>股票依個發仲ON9 間公司生意好唔好同股值有咩關係先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，冇人買話知你生意好唔好，你自己一個咪買飽佢睇佢升唔升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但偏偏就垃圾廢紙都有人搶"},{"pid":"0020a5a7e0565bb7c4fbca487e88a439cec4c77d","tid":486720,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-